{"kanda":6,"sarga":96,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"आर्तानांराक्षसीनांतुलङ्कायांवैकुलेकुले ।रावणःकरुणंशब्दंशुश्रावपरिदेवितम्","trans":"Ravana heard from every house in Lanka sounds of piteous cries and pathetic sounds of the afflicted.","words":[{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"लङ्कायाम्","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"कुलेकुले","m":"house after house"},{"d":"आर्तानाम्","m":"piteous cry"},{"d":"राक्षसीनाम्","m":"of Rakshasas"},{"d":"करुणम्","m":"pathetic"},{"d":"शब्दम्","m":"sound"},{"d":"परिदेवितम्","m":"of the afflicted"},{"d":"शुश्राव","m":"heard"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"स तुदीर्घंविनिःश्वस्यमुहूर्तंध्यानमास्थितः ।बभूवपरमक्रुद्धोरावणोभीमदर्शनः","trans":"Ravana remained silent for long, thought for a moment and assumed a terrific angry form.","words":[{"d":"सःरावणः","m":"that Ravana"},{"d":"दीर्घम्","m":"long"},{"d":"विनिःश्वस्य","m":"remaining silent"},{"d":"मुहूर्तम्","m":"for a moment"},{"d":"ध्यानम्","m":"in thought"},{"d":"आस्थितः","m":"assuming"},{"d":"परमक्रुद्धः","m":"angry"},{"d":"भीमदर्शनः","m":"of terrific form"},{"d":"बभूव","m":"appeared"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"सन्दश्यदशनैरोष्ठंक्रोधसम्रक्तलोचनः ।राक्षसैरपिदुर्दर्शःकालाग्निरिवमूर्छितः","trans":"Biting his teeth, eyes turned red in wrath, Ravana was perplexed. He was difficult to look at even for the Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"ओष्ठम्","m":"teeth"},{"d":"सन्दश्य","m":"eyes"},{"d":"क्रोधसम्रक्तलोचनः","m":"eyes turned red in wrath"},{"d":"मूर्छितः","m":"perplexed कालाग्निरिव like death form"},{"d":"राक्षसैरपि","m":"even for the Rakshasas"},{"d":"दुर्दर्शः","m":"difficult to look"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"उवाच च समीपस्थान्राक्षसान्राक्षसेश्वरः ।क्रोधाव्यक्तकथस्तत्रनिर्दहन्निवचक्षुषा महोदरंमहापार्श्वंविरूपाक्षं च राक्षसम् ।शीघ्रंवदतसैन्यानिनिर्यातेतिममाज्ञया","trans":"Thus spoke the Lord of Rakshasas indistinctly in anger with his eyes burning as though it would consume them (Rakshasas). He commanded Mahodara, Mahaparsva and Virupaksha who stood nearby saying\" quickly instruct the army to go.\"","words":[{"d":"क्रोधाव्यक्तरथः","m":"indistinct in anger"},{"d":"राक्षसेश्वरः","m":"Lord of Rakshasas"},{"d":"चक्षुषा","m":"eyes"},{"d":"निर्धहन्निव","m":"as if burning them"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"समीपस्थान्","m":"nearby"},{"d":"महोदरम्","m":"Mahodara"},{"d":"महापार्श्वम्","m":"Mahaparsva"},{"d":"राक्षसम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"विरूपाक्षम्","m":"Virupaksha"},{"d":"समीपस्थान्","m":"close by"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"आज्ञया","m":"order"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"निर्यातइति","m":"thus commanded"},{"d":"सैन्यानि","m":"the army"},{"d":"वदत","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"उवाच च समीपस्थान्राक्षसान्राक्षसेश्वरः ।क्रोधाव्यक्तकथस्तत्रनिर्दहन्निवचक्षुषा महोदरंमहापार्श्वंविरूपाक्षं च राक्षसम् ।शीघ्रंवदतसैन्यानिनिर्यातेतिममाज्ञया","trans":"Thus spoke the Lord of Rakshasas indistinctly in anger with his eyes burning as though it would consume them (Rakshasas). He commanded Mahodara, Mahaparsva and Virupaksha who stood nearby saying\" quickly instruct the army to go.\"","words":[{"d":"क्रोधाव्यक्तरथः","m":"indistinct in anger"},{"d":"राक्षसेश्वरः","m":"Lord of Rakshasas"},{"d":"चक्षुषा","m":"eyes"},{"d":"निर्धहन्निव","m":"as if burning them"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"समीपस्थान्","m":"nearby"},{"d":"महोदरम्","m":"Mahodara"},{"d":"महापार्श्वम्","m":"Mahaparsva"},{"d":"राक्षसम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"विरूपाक्षम्","m":"Virupaksha"},{"d":"समीपस्थान्","m":"close by"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"आज्ञया","m":"order"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"निर्यातइति","m":"thus commanded"},{"d":"सैन्यानि","m":"the army"},{"d":"वदत","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"तस्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वाराक्षसास्तेभयार्दिताः ।चोदयामासुरव्यग्रान्राक्षसांस्तान्नृपाज्ञया","trans":"On hearing the words of the king's order, the Rakshasas stricken with fear, unagitated, started thinking.","words":[{"d":"तेराक्षसाः","m":"those Rakshasas"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"their"},{"d":"तत्","m":"those"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"भयार्दिताः","m":"stricken with fear"},{"d":"अव्यग्रान्","m":"unagitated"},{"d":"तान्","m":"they"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasa's"},{"d":"नृपाज्ञया","m":"king's order"},{"d":"चोदयामासुः","m":"started thinking"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"तेतुसर्वेतथेत्युक्त्वाराक्षसाभीमदर्शनाः ।कृतस्वस्त्वयनाःसर्वेतेरणाभिमुखाययुः","trans":"All the Rakshasas with frightful looks saying 'Be it so', having prepared themselves with armor went towards the battlefield.","words":[{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"of them"},{"d":"भीमदर्शनाः","m":"with frightful looks"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"तथेति","m":"Be it so"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"saying"},{"d":"कृतस्वस्त्वनाः","m":"having prepared themselves with armor"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"रणाभिमुखाः","m":"towards the battlefield"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"प्रतिपूज्ययथान्यायंरावणंतेमहारथाः ।तस्थुःप्राञ्जलयःसर्वेभर्तुर्विजयकाङ्क्षिणः","trans":"All the great chariot warrior spraying to Ravana with folded palms stood desiring success.","words":[{"d":"महारथाः","m":"great chariot warriors"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"प्राञ्जलयः","m":"with folded palms"},{"d":"भर्तुः","m":"Lord"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"अथोवाचप्रहस्यैतान्रावणःक्रोधमूर्छितः ।महोदरमहापार्श्वौविरूपाक्षं च राक्षसम्","trans":"Then Ravana who was deluded with anger, laughing aloud spoke to Mahodara, Mahaparsva and Virupaksha.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"क्रोथमूर्छितः","m":"deluded with anger"},{"d":"प्रहस्य","m":"laughing aloud"},{"d":"एतान्","m":"these"},{"d":"राक्षसम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"विरूपाक्षं च","m":"and Virupaksha"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"अद्यबाणैर्धनुर्मुक्स्सैर्युगान्तादित्यसन्निभैः ।राघवंलक्ष्मणंचैवनेष्यामियमसादनम्","trans":"Loosening the shafts from the bow, Ravana resembling the Sun at the time of dissolution of the universe said,\" I shall dispatch Raghava and Lakshmana to the abode of the Lord of death.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"धनुर्मुक्तै","m":"loosened from the bow:"},{"d":"बाणैः","m":"shafts"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणंचैव","m":"and Lakshmana"},{"d":"यमसादनम्","m":"the abode of Yama the god of death"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"खरस्यकुम्भकर्णस्यप्रहसेन्द्रजितोस्तथा ।करिष्यामिप्रतीकारमद्यशत्रुवधादहम्","trans":"\"Today by the killing the enemy I will take my revenge and also of Khara, Kumbhakarna, Prahastha and Indrajith.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"शत्रुवधात्","m":"by the killing of enemy"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"खरस्य","m":"Khara's"},{"d":"कुम्बकर्णस्य","m":"Kumbhakarn's"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"प्रहस्तेन्द्रजितोः","m":"Prahastha, Indrajith"},{"d":"प्रतीकारम्","m":"revenge"},{"d":"करिष्यामि","m":"will take"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"नैवान्तरिक्षं न दिशो न नद्यौर्नापिसागराः ।प्रकाशत्वंगमिष्यन्तिमद्बाणजलदावृताः","trans":"\"By my arrows covering the sky like clouds there will be no effulgence both in space and in the quarters and not even in the ocean.\"","words":[{"d":"मद्बाणजलदावृताः","m":"my arrows like the clouds cover"},{"d":"अन्तरिक्षम्","m":"the sky"},{"d":"प्रकाशत्वम्","m":"the effulgence"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"दिशः","m":"directions"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"द्यौः","m":"both"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"सागराःअपि","m":"even the ocean"},{"d":"न गमिष्यन्ति","m":"not move"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"अद्यवानरमुख्यानांतानियूथानिभागशः ।धनुषाशरजालेनवधिष्यामिपतत्रिणा","trans":"\"Today by the network of plumed arrows released from my bow I shall kill the troops of Vanara leaders' part by part.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"धनुषा","m":"from my bow"},{"d":"पतत्रतिणा","m":"plumed arrows"},{"d":"शरजालेन","m":"network of arrows"},{"d":"वानरमुख्यानाम्","m":"Vanara leaders"},{"d":"यूथानि","m":"troops"},{"d":"भागशः","m":"part by part"},{"d":"वधिष्यामि","m":"will kill"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"अद्यवानरसैन्यानिरथेनपवनौजसा ।धनुस्समुद्रादुद्भूतैर्मथिष्यामिशरोर्मिभिः","trans":"\"Seated on the chariot I shall knock out the Vanara army by the waves in the form of arrows released from the ocean of my bow.\"","words":[{"d":"पवनौजसा","m":"as the wind"},{"d":"रथेन","m":"on the chariot"},{"d":"धनुःसमुद्रात्","m":"ocean of bow"},{"d":"शरोर्मिभिः","m":"in the shape of arrows"},{"d":"वानरसैन्यानि","m":"Vanara army"},{"d":"मथिष्यामि","m":"knock"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"व्याकोशपद्मवक्त्राणिपद्मकेसरवर्चसाम् ।अद्ययूथतटाकानिगजवत्प्रमथाम्यहम्","trans":"\"Like an elephant now I shall torment the ponds in the form of battalions of Vanaras shining like the filaments of lotuses, with their faces resembling open lotuses.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"now"},{"d":"व्याकोशपद्मवक्त्राणि","m":"their faces resembling open lotuses"},{"d":"पद्मकेसरवर्चसाम्","m":"filaments of lotuses"},{"d":"यूथतटाकानि","m":"ponds in the form of battalions"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"गजवत्","m":"elephant like"},{"d":"प्रमथामि","m":"tormenting"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"सशरैरद्यवदनैस्सङ्ख्येवानरयूथपाः ।मण्डयिष्यन्तिवसुधांसनालैरिवपङ्कजैः","trans":"\"Now with the arrows fixed on their faces the Vanara battalions spread on the earth will adorn the earth like lotuses spread on earth.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"now"},{"d":"वानरयूथपाः","m":"Vanara battalions"},{"d":"सशरैः","m":"the arrows"},{"d":"वदनैः","m":"faces"},{"d":"सनालैः","m":"fixed"},{"d":"पङ्कजैरिव","m":"like lotuses"},{"d":"वसुधाम्","m":"on earth"},{"d":"मण्डयिष्यन्ति","m":"will adorn"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"अद्ययूथप्रचण्डानांहरीणांद्रुमयोधिनाम् ।मुक्तेनैकेषुणायुद्धेभेत्स्यामि च शतंशतम्","trans":"\"Today in the combat each one of the arrows released by me will pierce through one hundred monkeys vehemently fighting with trees\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in combat"},{"d":"मुक्तेन","m":"released"},{"d":"एकेषुणा","m":"each one"},{"d":"यूथप्रचण्डानाम्","m":"troops vehemently"},{"d":"द्रुमयोधिनाम्","m":"fighting with trees"},{"d":"हरीणाम्","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"शतंशतम्","m":"one hundred each"},{"d":"भेत्स्यामि","m":"pierce through them"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"हतोभर्ताहतोभ्रातायासां च चतनयोहतः ।वधेनाद्यरिपोस्तासांकरोम्यश्रुप्रमार्जनम्","trans":"\"Today through the destruction of the enemy I will wipe the tears of the one whose son has been killed, whose brother has been killed.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"रिपोः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"वधेन","m":"by destruction"},{"d":"तासां","m":"his"},{"d":"भ्राता","m":"brother"},{"d":"यासाम्","m":"whose"},{"d":"तनयः","m":"brother"},{"d":"हतः","m":"killed"},{"d":"तासाम्","m":"whose"},{"d":"अश्रुप्रमार्जनम्","m":"wipe the tears"},{"d":"करोमि","m":"will do"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"अद्यमद्भाणनिर्भिन्नैःप्रकीर्णैर्गतचेतनैः ।करोमिवानरैर्युद्धेयत्नावेक्ष्यतलांमहीम्","trans":"\"Today, in the combat, my arrows will split open the Vanaras and ceased of life, they will be covering the earth. It will be possible to see the ground only with effort.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in combat"},{"d":"मद्बाणनिर्भिन्नैः","m":"by my arrows split open"},{"d":"गतचेतनैः","m":"ceased of life"},{"d":"प्रस्तीर्णैः","m":"spread out"},{"d":"वानरैः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"महीम्","m":"earth"},{"d":"यत्नावेक्ष्यतलाम्","m":"only with effort to see"},{"d":"करोमि","m":"make"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"अद्यगोमयवोगृध्राश्चये च मांसाशिनोऽपरे ।सर्वांस्तांस्तर्पयिष्यामिशत्रुमांसैश्शरार्दितैः","trans":"\"Today I shall provide for whatever animals, eagles or flesheating animals the flesh of enemies killed by my arrows.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"गोमायव:","m":"whatever animalsगृध्राश्च eagles"},{"d":"मांसाशिनः","m":"flesh eating animals"},{"d":"ये","m":"those"},{"d":"अपरे","m":"enemy"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"शरार्दितैः","m":"killed by my arrows"},{"d":"शत्रुमांसैः","m":"enemy's flesh"},{"d":"तर्पयिष्यामि","m":"will provide"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"कल्प्यतांमेरथंशीघ्रंक्षिप्रमानीयतांधनुः ।अनुप्रयान्तुमांयुद्धेयेऽत्रशिष्टानिशाचराः","trans":"\"Let my chariot and bow be ready and brought here. Let the night rangers who survived follow me.\"","words":[{"d":"मे","m":"I"},{"d":"रथः","m":"chariot"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"कल्प्यताम्","m":"be ready"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"क्षिप्रम्","m":"instantly"},{"d":"अनीयताम्","m":"brought"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"here"},{"d":"शिष्टाः","m":"survived"},{"d":"ये","m":"those"},{"d":"निशाचराः","m":"night rangers"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in combat"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"अनुप्रयान्तु","m":"follow"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"तस्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वामहापार्श्वोऽब्रवीद्वचः ।बलाध्यक्षान् स्थिथांस्तत्रबलंसंत्वर्यतामिति","trans":"On hearing the speech of Ravana, Mahaparsva enjoined the mighty leaders of the army standing there and spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"तत् वचनम्","m":"the speech of Ravana"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"स्थितान्","m":"standing"},{"d":"बलाध्यक्षान्","m":"mighty leaders"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"of army"},{"d":"संत्वर्यताम्","m":"enjoined"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"बलाध्यक्षास्तुसम्रब्दाराक्षसांस्तान् गृहेगृहे ।चोदयन्तःपरिययुर्लङ्कांलघुपराक्रमाः","trans":"\"Let the army leaders of mighty valour go hurriedly to search in every house in Lanka for Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"लघुपराक्रमाः","m":"mighty valour"},{"d":"बलाध्यक्षान्तु","m":"army chief"},{"d":"सम्रब्दाः","m":"hurriedly"},{"d":"गृहेगृहे","m":"house to house"},{"d":"तान्","m":"they"},{"d":"राक्षसान्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"चोदयन्तः","m":"searched"},{"d":"लङ्काम्","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"परिययुः","m":"went"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"ततोमुहूर्तान्निष्पेतूराक्षसाभीमदर्शनाः ।नदन्तोभीमवदनानानाप्रहरणैर्भुजैः असिभिःपट्टसै: शूलैर्गदाभिर्मुसलैर्हलैः ।शक्तिभिस्तीक्ष्णधाराभिर्महद्भि: कूटमुद्गरैः यष्टिभिर्विमलैश्चक्रैर्निशितैश्चपरश्वथै: ।भिन्दिपालैःशतघ्नीभिरन्यैश्चापिवरायुधैः","trans":"Then the Rakshasas of terrific looks, and frightening faces holding on shoulders roaring departed with swords, spears, tridents, maces, iron bars, halas, sharp pointed javelins, huge Kutamudgaras, staffs and several discusses, sharp Bhindipalas, Sataghnis and many kinds of excellent weapons.","w